history.text: hi

Hi! 
Do you like Animation movies?
Yes, I do. Computer animated, haddrwan, stop motion, anything
Have you ever seen Toy Story?
Yes, I was interested to see it, but never saw it
What is the story of Toy Story ?
It is a great movie, about toys who come to life when their owners aren't presnet
The two main toys are a cowboy doll and a astronaut action figure
it there an explanation why they come to life ?
I don't know, but it might explain on their website.
Pixar website, I mean
But it not a plot point in the movie. It is ok, a movie should not explain everything. What kind of animation is this movie ?
It was released in 1995 as the first feature length computer animated film.

It was also the first film produced
 by Pixar
I find computer animated film sterile and lifeless, how to you did you find the movie visually ?
I thought it was very believable, and the toys appeared to be truly alive
I think it helped that they brought the character of the toys into the film
I will trust you on that anything else that you find great about this film ?
So , in the beginning of he film, Woody is Andy's favorite toy

what is the personall
ty of Woody?

Woody is a Sheriff doll, and is the leader of all the other toys. 
Then Andy has a birthday party and receives an astronaut toy, Buzz Lightyear
Buzz becomes the new favorite, and Woody gets jealous
Does it gets dramatic or funny ?
A little of both. Woody ends up accidentally knocking Buzz out the window, and the other toys rebel against Woody.
What happens to Woody ?
He gets taken to Pizza Planet with his owner, but on the way he and Buzz get in a fight at the gas station, and then they get left behind
So there is a lot of action in this movie ?
Buzz is convinced he is a real space ranger, and he and Woody get stuck in a crane game, and taken to Andy's neighbor's house, Sid.
I don't know how much action you would consider it to have, but it is an adventure.

I did not know it was an adventure movie. I could have been a drama with just toys talking about themselves. As for the movie,  h
ow is Sid ?
Sid is a bit mischevious, and has a dog, Scud, that chases after them
How does the chase end ?
They escape Sid's house and are chasing after Andy's moving truck, and Scud chases after them
Buzz saves Woody from Scud, and Woody uses Andy's RC car to rescue him.
There is a lot of action, I I like this
How does the film end ?
It is a really great movie, Rotten Tomatoes gives it a 100% rating
It ends with the toys back with Andy at his new house.
How do you rate the movie personally ?
It is one of my favorite movies
Good, You convinced me to see it.
Great!
Thanks for chatting today!

Than
ks and have a good day.
You too
bye
